# what is cloning
cloning means donloading a copy of your repo to your machine.

#steps in cloning a repo

-first copy the repo URL
-Open terminal/command prompt(on windows, open Gitbash,CMD, or powershell, for mac, open termial, and for Linux, open your terminal)
-Go to the folder you want
-Run the clone command
-and finally enter the project folder

##Reasons for cloning
-to be able to work on hr code locally
-contribute to the project
-get full history
-work offline
and mosot importantly, backup the repo
